articles.title: ICC World Cup 2023: Who’ll win South Africa vs Bangladesh match? Prediction, fantasy team, pitch report and more | Mint - Mint
articles.description: While South Africa has a strong record against Bangladesh historically, recent encounters have favoured Bangladesh.
articles.content: South Africa have won 3 out of their 4 matches so far in the ICC World Cup 2023. In all the victories, they batted first and put up massive scores, twice beyond 300 (one 399) and once beyond 400. The… [+3092 chars]
